    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to list this beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s been my pride and joy and has been totally babied since day one. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014garage-kept, sparkling clean, and looks just like it did the day it left the showroom! If you\u2019re looking for that perfect, 'like-new' feel, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it. Shoot me a message if you want to come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
