      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. It has been my pride and joy and has lived its whole life tucked away in a climate-controlled garage, so it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you're looking for something that's been totally babied and is in truly flawless shape, this is the one for you. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or dent\u2014it\u2019s just perfect. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love with how it drives!",
